Name: Fisher
Description: The Division of Fisher consists of part of the Sunshine Coast Regional Council.
ProductsAndIndustry: Health care, retail, tourism, education and construction and development are the major employers. Other industries include pineapple, orchard and flower crops, dairy and beef cattle farming, and horse racing.
NameDerivation: Named in honour of Andrew Fisher, 1862-1928, Prime Minister of Australia (1908-09, 1910-13, 1914-15) and a Member of the House of Representatives (1901-15).
